  "keyFeatures": [
    "One-command deployment script for quick setup",
    "Optimized PHP 8.2-FPM Alpine image with Moodle-specific extensions",
    "PostgreSQL 16 database with persistent storage",
    "Nginx reverse proxy with FastCGI configuration",
    "Automated cron job execution for Moodle maintenance tasks",
    "Pre-configured PHP settings optimized for Moodle (512M memory, large uploads)",
    "Docker Compose orchestration with service dependencies",
    "Automatic Moodle 4.3 download and installation"
