    "docker-compose.yml - Service orchestration (db, app, cron, web)",
    "Dockerfile - Custom PHP-FPM image with extensions",
    "nginx/Default.conf - Web server configuration",
    "Environment variables: SITE_URL, DB_NAME, DB_USER, DB_PASS",
    "Volume mounts: ./html (Moodle code), ./moodledata (uploads), ./db_data (PostgreSQL)"
